{"tid":2348174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衞生署出錯！3座大廈不符強制檢測準則被錯誤列入名單，今日發現錯誤剔除。張竹君致歉","createTime":"2020-12-31T14:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T06:01:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c75d6da0f3a26f518325f12b3be4d411e9872d2","tid":2348174,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201231/s00001/32ff4a67c3da5a2d67c8dfeea28f7cfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201231%2Fs00001%2F32ff4a67c3da5a2d67c8dfeea28f7cfc.jpg&h=e8cff43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府日前宣布收緊大廈強制檢測準則，昨刊憲要求43幢大廈居民強制檢測。衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今在疫情記者會稱，翻查紀錄後，發現當中3幢大廈並不符合兩單位兩無關連個案的準則，例如一些患者不在該單位居住一段時間，或已更改地址，因此會在強制檢測名單中被剔除。衛生防護中心會檢討如何改善，並對市民造成的不便和混亂致歉。<br />\n<br />\n3幢被剔除強制檢測名單大廈：<br />\n．觀塘曉麗苑曉星閣<br />\n．寶琳翠林邨安林樓<br />\n．青衣青華苑華欣閣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20201231/s00001/1609403005226/新冠肺炎-今增68確診18宗源頭不明-3大廈不屬強檢被剔除-張竹君致歉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201231%2Fs00001%2F1609403005226%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A2%9E68%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA18%E5%AE%97%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-3%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%AC%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%94%E9%99%A4-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=e5a9b85e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20201231%2Fs00001%2F1609403005226%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A2%9E68%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA18%E5%AE%97%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E-3%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%AC%E5%BC%B7%E6%AA%A2%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%94%E9%99%A4-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89&h=98d5e619\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20201231/s00001/16094030